Interface NexusService.ObjectResponse

Enclosing interface:
NexusService
public static interface NexusService.ObjectResponse
extends Streamable

If the object returned in a Callback contains any NexusObjects, the returned object must implement this interface and provide a reference to the contained objects. This is necessary for Nexus to register the objects with the system when they are received over the network.
